When working with JavaScript and CSS in the BioBuddy project:

## JavaScript Best Practices

- Use modern JavaScript features (ES6+)
- Implement proper error handling
- Use meaningful function and variable names
- Add comments for complex logic
- Follow existing code patterns

## CSS Styling

- Use the Argon Design System color palette
- Primary color: `#5e72e4`
- Success color: `#2dce89`
- Maintain consistent spacing and typography
- Use Bootstrap classes when available
- Follow existing naming conventions

## BioBuddy Specific

- Integrate with Shiny reactive system when needed
- Use Font Awesome icons consistently
- Maintain responsive design principles
- Follow the established UI/UX patterns
- Test across different browsers

## Performance

- Minimize DOM manipulations
- Use efficient selectors
- Optimize CSS for performance
- Avoid blocking operations